  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 99-3-47, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO INCLUDE MISDEMEANOR WARRANTS WITHIN THE PROVISION OF LAW THAT PROVIDES FOR ELECTRONIC WARRANTS; TO CLARIFY THAT A SIGNATURE UTILIZED BY THE JUDICIAL BRANCH OF STATE GOVERNMENT ON A PROTECTION ORDER SHALL NOT BE DENIED LEGAL EFFECT OR ENFORCEABILITY SOLELY BECAUSE IT IS IN ELECTRONIC FORM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
